ComicInfo.Summary: "DOUBLE TROUBLE" Introducing America's Newest Teen Idol, Liberty Lad! When Minuteman is arrested for crimes he didn't commit, it's up to the star-spangled squirt and his compatriots to clear their fearless leader's name before the city falls at the hands of Déjà Vu's deadly army of doppelgangers! Plus, Pinstripe is back for a final showdown, but as the team faces off with the dapper don, a mysterious stranger stands in their way. Will he be friend or foe?
